org.apache.juneau.rest.response

Class EarlyHints

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.rest.response.HttpResponse
      • org.apache.juneau.rest.response.EarlyHints

  • @Response(code=103,
          description="Early Hints")
public class EarlyHints
extends HttpResponse
    Represents an HTTP 103 Early Hints response.

    Used to return some response headers before final HTTP message.
